{"tid":942710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係懲罰勤力既人","createTime":"2018-12-16T03:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T04:02:30.000Z","uid":126036,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64b220a8d7a44b295e833fd1868f0727fa41127d","tid":942710,"uid":126036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"我相信好多香港人都係咁<br />\n<br />\n無父幹出身基層，努力讀書揹住學債向上爬到中層，私樓供得起但無首期，公屋無份居屋抽唔中，稅又要交但一滴福利都無。<br />\n<br />\n相反，懶人拎綜援上公屋無負擔，享用福利。<br />\n<br />\n點解，點解要交稅養班懶人，勤力既人乜都無仲要係身上拎，活係香港真係好辛苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ace7fbbde0e9a95ae37d9b6439ee6f3fcaa55c","tid":942710,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"賣礦機 sell倫敦金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3face3572a839ffa1644cbfe8e367a7ae3871d14","tid":942710,"uid":92278,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"牛夠勤力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066670a4b79e30ce931d73838ea6585ef753de58","tid":942710,"uid":126036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3face3572a839ffa1644cbfe8e367a7ae3871d14","tid":942710,"uid":92278,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"牛夠勤力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"所以港奴鍾意返工唔敢反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}